00:00:53.829 --> 00:00:56.070
What are the causes of these risks?

00:00:56.070 --> 00:01:01.679
Damage to your skin can arise in any situation
where direct or indirect exposure is possible,

00:01:01.679 --> 00:01:02.260
for example

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:08.350
6. Immersing hands in hazardous materials
7. Splashes, aerosols and dusts landing on

00:01:08.350 --> 00:01:12.540
the skin
8. Where there is no containment or reduction

00:01:12.540 --> 00:01:15.720
in use
9. Where there is poor or no extraction at

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:19.210
the source
10. Where staff do not have suitable protective

00:01:19.210 --> 00:01:23.570
