11. Have the wrong or poorly maintained protective

00:01:23.570 --> 00:01:27.170
clothing
12. Not knowing how to put on or take off

00:01:27.170 --> 00:01:31.100
gloves safely
13. Poor house keeping and storage of chemicals

00:01:31.100 --> 00:01:32.899
or hazardous substances

00:01:32.899 --> 00:01:33.579
And where there is a

00:01:33.579 --> 00:01:40.579
